00:32:19,760 --> 00:32:20,890
I heard you're back.

582
00:32:22,320 --> 00:32:23,360
Who's that?

583
00:32:29,080 --> 00:32:30,200
What happened to Ju'er?

584
00:32:30,200 --> 00:32:30,880
Don't ask.

585
00:32:31,080 --> 00:32:32,160
Go see her quickly.

586
00:32:32,760 --> 00:32:33,200
Okay.

587
00:32:34,200 --> 00:32:34,800
Ju'er.

588
00:32:43,960 --> 00:32:44,680
Ju'er.

589
00:32:46,920 --> 00:32:47,400
Ju'er!

590
00:32:48,800 --> 00:32:49,640
What's wrong?

591
00:32:50,000 --> 00:32:50,860
What happened?

592
00:32:52,320 --> 00:32:53,580
Did someone bully you?

593
00:32:54,400 --> 00:32:55,440
Was it Long Xia?

594
00:32:57,360 --> 00:32:57,880
No.

595
00:32:58,120 --> 00:32:59,720
Was it the Japanese?

596
00:33:05,840 --> 00:33:07,200
Japanese?

597
00:33:09,280 --> 00:33:10,540
Which Japanese person

598
00:33:10,960 --> 00:33:12,680
dared to bully our family?

599
00:33:13,400 --> 00:33:14,440
Tell me who it was.

600
00:33:14,720 --> 00:33:16,050
I'll go to Captain Inoue

601
00:33:16,120 --> 00:33:17,320
and ask him to help us.

602
00:33:27,160 --> 00:33:28,090
What's going on?

603
00:33:32,120 --> 00:33:34,050
Are you trying to worry me to death?

604
00:33:40,800 --> 00:33:42,660
The one who bullied your daughter

605
00:33:44,520 --> 00:33:46,240
is Captain Inoue himself.

606
00:34:09,239 --> 00:34:10,170
Let's stop here.

607
00:34:13,639 --> 00:34:15,040
I'll drop you off here then.

608
00:34:15,040 --> 00:34:17,120
I need to go to the police station anyway.

609
00:34:17,120 --> 00:34:19,000
What are you going to do at the police station?

610
00:34:19,000 --> 00:34:21,080
You don't quite understand the Japanese character.

611
00:34:21,080 --> 00:34:23,080
They're all trained to face failure.

612
00:34:23,080 --> 00:34:24,239
So when it comes to something,

613
00:34:24,239 --> 00:34:25,699
they never give up easily.

614
00:34:26,880 --> 00:34:28,400
So what are you going to do?

615
00:34:28,560 --> 00:34:29,320
What I can do

616
00:34:29,719 --> 00:34:30,480
is to quickly start

617
00:34:30,480 --> 00:34:32,480
investigating Dakaku Mineo's plane crash,

618
00:34:32,480 --> 00:34:34,199
bring you into my work system,

619
00:34:34,360 --> 00:34:35,820
and clear your suspicion.

620
00:34:36,840 --> 00:34:37,969
Starting tomorrow,

621
00:34:38,520 --> 00:34:40,120
you need to start visiting people

622
00:34:40,120 --> 00:34:41,239
and try to get

623
00:34:41,480 --> 00:34:43,560
information about the messenger from the villagers.

624
00:34:43,560 --> 00:34:44,360
I understand.

625
00:34:45,320 --> 00:34:46,280
The Special Police Unit

626
00:34:46,280 --> 00:34:48,340
won't dare to investigate me openly.

627
00:34:48,639 --> 00:34:49,920
But their investigation of you,

628
00:34:49,920 --> 00:34:51,560
although we disrupted it today,

629
00:34:51,560 --> 00:34:52,960
they still won't give up.

630
00:34:53,000 --> 00:34:54,530
So you must be very careful.

631
00:34:54,679 --> 00:34:55,940
What should we do then?

632
00:34:56,040 --> 00:34:57,480
I'm going to the police station now

633
00:34:57,480 --> 00:34:59,040
to put some pressure on them.

634
00:34:59,040 --> 00:35:00,520
Hopefully under pressure,

635
00:35:00,520 --> 00:35:03,120
they'll postpone their investigation of you.

636
00:35:03,320 --> 00:35:03,920
But if they

637
00:35:03,920 --> 00:35:05,520
keep focusing on Tang Ju'er,

638
00:35:06,040 --> 00:35:06,600
for us,

639
00:35:06,600 --> 00:35:07,760
that's the most dangerous sign.

640
00:35:07,760 --> 00:35:08,960
I've instructed her.

641
00:35:09,400 --> 00:35:10,600
She won't say anything.

642
00:35:10,600 --> 00:35:11,400
Let's hope so.

643
00:35:13,200 --> 00:35:14,530
After you go back today,

644
00:35:15,360 --> 00:35:17,000
have a good talk with your father

645
00:35:17,000 --> 00:35:19,000
and try to ease the tension with him.

646
00:35:19,160 --> 00:35:21,160
We need a stable base,

647
00:35:21,280 --> 00:35:22,040
so that we can

648
00:35:22,040 --> 00:35:24,440
find the messenger's whereabouts faster.

649
00:35:25,000 --> 00:35:25,880
I know.

650
00:35:26,360 --> 00:35:26,760
Go now.

651
00:35:27,360 --> 00:35:29,090
I'll come pick you up tomorrow.

652
00:35:55,040 --> 00:35:55,770
Here, Major.

653
00:35:56,680 --> 00:35:57,940
Have something to eat.

654
00:36:01,640 --> 00:36:04,040
There was a lot of commotion outside today.

655
00:36:05,240 --> 00:36:07,300
Seems we can't stay here much longer.

656
00:36:13,760 --> 00:36:15,280
I've already sent word

657
00:36:15,400 --> 00:36:17,260
to Macau about your whereabouts.

658
00:36:17,320 --> 00:36:19,920
They'll find a way to contact the Nationalist government

659
00:36:19,920 --> 00:36:21,980
and send someone as soon as possible.

660
00:36:22,240 --> 00:36:22,760
Good.

661
00:36:24,120 --> 00:36:26,120
But there's one problem now.

662
00:36:27,280 --> 00:36:28,740
My daughter has returned.

663
00:36:33,440 --> 00:36:35,840
Your daughter coming back at this time -

664
00:36:37,240 --> 00:36:40,300
could she be connected to the Nationalist government?

665
00:36:41,320 --> 00:36:44,180
She couldn't possibly have any dealings with them.

666
00:36:44,760 --> 00:36:46,400
The problem is

667
00:36:47,360 --> 00:36:49,640
she's returned with a Japanese officer.

668
00:36:50,520 --> 00:36:51,650
A Japanese officer?

669
00:36:55,120 --> 00:36:56,360
That is troublesome.

670
00:36:59,680 --> 00:37:00,280
All right.

671
00:37:00,680 --> 00:37:02,080
I'll handle this matter.

672
00:37:03,080 --> 00:37:03,960
You should rest well.

673
00:37:03,960 --> 00:37:05,220
Have something to eat.

674
00:37:20,720 --> 00:37:21,650
Mother-in-law.

675
00:37:22,480 --> 00:37:23,940
Is Dad still angry with me?

676
00:37:24,560 --> 00:37:26,000
He's just upset

677
00:37:26,160 --> 00:37:27,820
for the moment. It'll be fine.

678
00:37:28,240 --> 00:37:29,170
Mother-in-law.

679
00:37:30,080 --> 00:37:31,560
I bought a gift for Dad.

680
00:37:32,040 --> 00:37:32,360
That's nice.

681
00:37:32,360 --> 00:37:33,480
Should I give it to him now

682
00:37:33,480 --> 00:37:34,810
or wait until tomorrow?

683
00:37:35,560 --> 00:37:36,360
How about this:

684
00:37:36,360 --> 00:37:37,880
could you give it to him for me later?

685
00:37:37,880 --> 00:37:39,680
You should give it to him yourself.

686
00:37:39,680 --> 00:37:40,160
I'm afraid he's still mad at me.

687
00:37:40,160 --> 00:37:40,760
Ying'er.

688
00:37:41,160 --> 00:37:41,760
Come here.

689
00:37:46,000 --> 00:37:47,200
It's alright. Go on.

690
00:37:51,520 --> 00:37:52,080
Dad.

691
00:38:00,360 --> 00:38:01,880
Auntie, please sit.

692
00:38:11,520 --> 00:38:13,250
Do you think you deserve to sit?

693
00:38:24,280 --> 00:38:26,010
The whole family is here today.

694
00:38:26,760 --> 00:38:28,200
So in front of everyone,

695
00:38:28,320 --> 00:38:29,850
explain yourself clearly.

696
00:38:30,000 --> 00:38:31,760
What exactly is your relationship

697
00:38:31,760 --> 00:38:33,360
with that Japanese officer?

698
00:38:35,240 --> 00:38:36,120
Wumu.

699
00:38:38,720 --> 00:38:39,780
He is a good person.

700
00:38:40,000 --> 00:38:40,520
Wumu?

701
00:38:40,520 --> 00:38:42,320
I don't care if he's good or bad.

702
00:38:42,440 --> 00:38:43,360
I just want you to tell me

703
00:38:43,360 --> 00:38:44,690
how you came to know him.

704
00:38:44,880 --> 00:38:45,920
How long have you known him?

705
00:38:45,920 --> 00:38:47,600
How far has your relationship progressed?

706
00:38:47,600 --> 00:38:49,160
It's not what you think between us.

707
00:38:49,160 --> 00:38:49,760
Yingying,

708
00:38:50,480 --> 00:38:52,140
speak properly to your father

709
00:38:52,680 --> 00:38:54,080
and don't make him angry.

710
00:38:54,480 --> 00:38:56,640
Didn't you go north to pursue your ideals

711
00:38:56,640 --> 00:38:57,840
and your principles?

712
00:38:58,560 --> 00:39:01,360
How did you end up involved with that Japanese man?

713
00:39:01,600 --> 00:39:03,600
And what about that gun?

714
00:39:06,080 --> 00:39:06,560
Father,

715
00:39:07,760 --> 00:39:08,960
I was mistreated

716
00:39:09,680 --> 00:39:11,740
by the Japanese police this morning.

717
00:39:12,680 --> 00:39:13,880
Could you please not interrogate me

718
00:39:13,880 --> 00:39:15,200
like they did?

719
00:39:17,440 --> 00:39:18,640
Ying'er just came back today

720
00:39:18,640 --> 00:39:20,200
and was already mistreated at the police station.

721
00:39:20,200 --> 00:39:21,360
Why don't you let her rest

722
00:39:21,360 --> 00:39:22,160
and talk about this tomorrow?

723
00:39:22,160 --> 00:39:22,760
Shut up!

724
00:39:23,680 --> 00:39:24,880
Your sister's actions today

725
00:39:24,880 --> 00:39:26,360
have brought shame to our entire family.

726
00:39:26,360 --> 00:39:27,840
She has put our family in a position

727
00:39:27,840 --> 00:39:29,440
where everyone points fingers and criticizes us.

728
00:39:29,440 --> 00:39:31,240
And you're still defending her?

729
00:39:31,560 --> 00:39:32,090
Sit down!

730
00:39:35,520 --> 00:39:37,450
All information about this person

731
00:39:37,680 --> 00:39:38,880
is top secret.

732
00:39:39,560 --> 00:39:40,400
I swear

733
00:39:41,000 --> 00:39:42,330
that about this person,

734
00:39:42,760 --> 00:39:44,160
I won't say a single word.

735
00:39:45,480 --> 00:39:46,610
Will you talk or not?

736
00:39:47,160 --> 00:39:47,760
Yingying.

737
00:39:48,120 --> 00:39:49,160
Um, Yingying...

738
00:39:49,440 --> 00:39:51,500
Didn't you buy a gift for your father?

739
00:39:51,920 --> 00:39:53,240
Quick, take it out.

740
00:39:54,000 --> 00:39:55,200
Quickly, take it out.

741
00:39:55,280 --> 00:39:56,540
Give it to your father.

742
00:39:59,120 --> 00:40:00,560
Sir, please don't be angry anymore.

743
00:40:00,560 --> 00:40:00,880
Look,

744
00:40:00,880 --> 00:40:02,640
Yingying even bought you a gift.

745
00:40:02,640 --> 00:40:03,160
Look.

746
00:40:04,520 --> 00:40:06,180
Hurry, bring it to the master.

747
00:40:07,280 --> 00:40:07,880
Dad,

748
00:40:08,800 --> 00:40:10,080
this is for you.

749
00:40:14,080 --> 00:40:15,610
Are you going to talk or not?

750
00:40:16,040 --> 00:40:17,360
If you don't explain clearly,

751
00:40:17,360 --> 00:40:18,820
then get out of this house!

752
00:40:22,720 --> 00:40:23,800
Fine, I'll leave!

753
00:40:31,520 --> 00:40:32,600
Go follow your sister.

754
00:40:32,600 --> 00:40:34,660
Don't let her meet that Japanese man.

755
00:40:35,880 --> 00:40:37,200
Auntie, you go too.

756
00:40:37,760 --> 00:40:39,280
If she refuses to come back,

757
00:40:39,280 --> 00:40:40,920
let her stay at your place for the night.

758
00:40:40,920 --> 00:40:41,920
Keep her company.

759
00:40:42,120 --> 00:40:42,280
Alright.

760
00:40:42,280 --> 00:40:42,920
Hurry up.

761
00:40:43,280 --> 00:40:43,610
Okay.

762
00:41:44,120 --> 00:41:45,280
Dad is so angry.

763
00:41:46,360 --> 00:41:47,360
What should we do?

764
00:41:52,320 --> 00:41:53,320
You have no idea.

765
00:41:53,320 --> 00:41:54,840
During the years you've been gone,

766
00:41:54,840 --> 00:41:56,000
these Japanese came to the island

767
00:41:56,000 --> 00:41:57,800
and did so many terrible things.

768
00:41:58,520 --> 00:42:01,240
Later, Uncle wanted me and Dad to go to Macau,

769
00:42:01,600 --> 00:42:03,200
but Dad absolutely refused.

770
00:42:04,600 --> 00:42:05,680
Just look at yourself.

771
00:42:05,680 --> 00:42:06,680
Today, actually,

772
00:42:06,960 --> 00:42:09,280
Dad wasn't angry at you when he said those things.

773
00:42:09,280 --> 00:42:10,600
He was angry at the Japanese.

774
00:42:10,600 --> 00:42:11,400
I mean, really,

775
00:42:11,400 --> 00:42:12,960
you even brought a Japanese person to our home.

776
00:42:12,960 --> 00:42:14,360
How could he not be angry?

777
00:42:14,800 --> 00:42:16,160
I didn't want to either,

778
00:42:16,760 --> 00:42:17,820
but I had no choice.

779
00:42:18,760 --> 00:42:20,090
We had to come together.

780
00:42:26,400 --> 00:42:27,460
What are you doing?

781
00:42:28,240 --> 00:42:28,880
I got it.

782
00:42:31,000 --> 00:42:31,920
You're not as simple as you seem.
